section.section:
The authority shall promulgate regulations for the administration of the recognition award and scholarship programs. The regulations shall include but not be limited to the following:
Eligibility requirements which shall include requirements that students must be Kentucky citizens who have declared an intention to attend a participating institution;
Award selection criteria including but not limited to the student's rank in his class, grade-point average, leadership and service potential, and the submission of a written essay;
Award amounts;
Selection committee, qualifications and duties;
Fund distribution formula;
Application deadlines; and
Administrative procedures.
